536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some hospital staff arerefusing to clock inon the opening of the Olympics over working conditions.\", \"from\": 4538, \"to\": 4636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4595}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4599, \"to\": 4611}, {\"ngram\": \"working conditions\", \"from\": 4617, \"to\": 4635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the Olympics' top organisers in Paris toldRTLthat organisers will not ban people from striking 'to defend their rights', which is as French of a response as you can get.\", \"from\": 4638, \"to\": 4814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4677, \"end\": 4682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.090223790884818e-27, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics' top organisers\", \"from\": 4645, \"to\": 4673}, {\"ngram\": \"toldRTLthat organisers\", \"from\": 4683, \"to\": 4705}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4719, \"to\": 4725}, {\"ngram\": \"their rights\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4763}, {\"ngram\": \"a response\", \"from\": 4788, \"to\": 4798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking of, it's not just the thought of transport staff walking out that could impact how smoothly the Olympics go.\", \"from\": 4816, \"to\": 4933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the thought\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4854}, {\"ngram\": \"transport staff\", \"from\": 4858, \"to\": 4873}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4917, \"to\": 4929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several key exertions to the Paris Metro station that are part of the 'Grand Paris Express' are complete or underway.\", \"from\": 4935, \"to\": 5052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4964, \"end\": 4975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\", \"score\": 0.9999998407884176, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Metro\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_M\\u00e9tro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several key exertions\", \"from\": 4935, \"to\": 4956}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4993, \"to\": 4997}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'Grand Paris Express\", \"from\": 5001, \"to\": 5025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though the rest will not be ready until 2030, transit officials have said most lines do not service Olympic sites.\", \"from\": 5053, \"to\": 5167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 5060, \"to\": 5068}, {\"ngram\": \"transit officials\", \"from\": 5099, \"to\": 5116}, {\"ngram\": \"most lines\", \"from\": 5127, \"to\": 5137}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic sites\", \"from\": 5153, \"to\": 5166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Charles de Gaulle expressway, which will link the airport and the Gare de l'Est railway station, will not be ready, however.\", \"from\": 5169, \"to\": 5297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Charles de Gaulle expressway\", \"from\": 5169, \"to\": 5201}, {\"ngram\": \"the airport\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5230}, {\"ngram\": \"the Gare de l'Est railway station\", \"from\": 5235, \"to\": 5268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless of what Metro, bus, trams and suburb train lines are running, all will cost double what they normally do over the Olympics.\", \"from\": 5299, \"to\": 5433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 5318, \"to\": 5323}, {\"ngram\": \"bus\", \"from\": 5325, \"to\": 5328}, {\"ngram\": \"trams\", \"from\": 5330, \"to\": 5335}, {\"ngram\": \"suburb train lines\", \"from\": 5340, \"to\": 5358}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5420, \"to\": 5432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00cele-de-France Mobilit\\u00e9s, the local authority in charge of public transport companies, said this was needed so locals would not have to solely bear the cost of the influx of riders.\", \"from\": 5435, \"to\": 5615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00cele-de-France Mobilit\\u00e9s\", \"from\": 5435, \"to\": 5458}, {\"ngram\": \"the local authority\", \"from\": 5460, \"to\": 5479}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 5483, \"to\": 5489}, {\"ngram\": \"public transport companies\", \"from\": 5493, \"to\": 5519}, {\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 5545, \"to\": 5551}, {\"ngram\": \"the cost\", \"from\": 5582, \"to\": 5590}, {\"ngram\": \"the influx\", \"from\": 5594, \"to\": 5604}, {\"ngram\": \"riders\", \"from\": 5608, \"to\": 5614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they will have plenty of options.\", \"from\": 5617, \"to\": 5654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 5636, \"to\": 5642}, {\"ngram\": \"options\", \"from\": 5646, \"to\": 5653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"City officials hope to add 10,000 more bikes across some 60 'Olympistes' - cycle routes with getting between Olympic venues in mind.\", \"from\": 5655, \"to\": 5787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"City officials\", \"from\": 5655, \"to\": 5669}, {\"ngram\": \"10,000 more bikes\", \"from\": 5682, \"to\": 5699}, {\"ngram\": \"some 60 'Olympistes' - cycle routes\", \"from\": 5707, \"to\": 5742}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic venues\", \"from\": 5764, \"to\": 5778}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 5782, \"to\": 5786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is aiming to carry out the Olympics with 50% less planet-warming carbon emissions compared to London 2012 and Rio 2016.\", \"from\": 5789, \"to\": 5914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5789, \"end\": 5794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.090223790884818e-27, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 5889, \"end\": 5900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.31156622275