years\", \"from\": 6512, \"to\": 6531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the Russia-Ukraine war and the Covid pandemic to the violence that has seized Parisian streets in recent years.\", \"from\": 6533, \"to\": 6649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6542, \"end\": 6560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russo-Ukrainian_War\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russia-Ukraine war\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russo-Ukrainian_War\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russo-Ukrainian_War\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Covid pandemic\", \"from\": 6565, \"to\": 6583}, {\"ngram\": \"the violence\", \"from\": 6587, \"to\": 6599}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisian streets\", \"from\": 6616, \"to\": 6632}, {\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 6636, \"to\": 6648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'All these factors do not seem enough to prevent a successful summer of games,' he stressed.\", \"from\": 6651, \"to\": 6743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All these factors\", \"from\": 6652, \"to\": 6669}, {\"ngram\": \"a successful summer\", \"from\": 6700, \"to\": 6719}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 6723, \"to\": 6728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zoe Adjey, a senior lecturer in hospitality and tourism at the University of East London, told Metro.co.uk how a list of potential problems like the above is almost a guarantee when it comes to organising something as elaborate as the Olympics.\", \"from\": 6745, \"to\": 6989, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6745, \"end\": 6748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zoe_Slater\", \"score\": 0.8150257872198072, \"rank\": 0.2238010779517793, \"text\": \"Zoe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zoe_Slater\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zoe_Slater\"}, {\"begin\": 6840, \"end\": 6851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\", \"score\": 0.9993608704168107, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Metro.co.uk\", \"t