m\": 7195, \"to\": 7207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'One such scandal was the G4S debacle,' Adjey said, referring to the private security company that, only a month before the opening ceremony, admitted it would not be able to provide enough staff.\", \"from\": 7221, \"to\": 7417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One such scandal\", \"from\": 7222, \"to\": 7238}, {\"ngram\": \"the G4S debacle\", \"from\": 7243, \"to\": 7258}, {\"ngram\": \"Adjey\", \"from\": 7261, \"to\": 7266}, {\"ngram\": \"the private security company\", \"from\": 7286, \"to\": 7314}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 7341, \"to\": 7361}, {\"ngram\": \"enough staff\", \"from\": 7404, \"to\": 7416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The media was also filled with negativity surrounding sponsors like McDonald's and Coca-Cola, criticising them for promoting junk food.\", \"from\": 7419, \"to\": 7555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7503, \"end\": 7512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\", \"score\": 0.999999756109021, \"rank\": 2.43891147291647e-07, \"text\": \"Coca-Cola\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The media\", \"from\": 7420, \"to\": 7429}, {\"ngram\": \"negativity surrounding sponsors\", \"from\": 7451, \"to\": 7482}, {\"ngram\": \"McDonald\", \"from\": 7488, \"to\": 7496}, {\"ngram\": \"junk food\", \"from\": 7545, \"to\": 7554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'However, it is important to remember the moment when Her Majesty Queen Elizabeth II and James Bond parachuted into the Olympic Stadium in Stratford - at that instant, every one of those negative stories dissipated.'\", \"from\": 7557, \"to\": 7773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7611, \"end\": 7641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9734563619629713e-55, \"text\": \"Her Majesty Queen Elizabeth II\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\",